  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to analyses time to disease relapse of RA patients if TNF-α inhibitors are
      being tapered, the predictive factors that are associated with successful taper of TNF-α
      inhibitors. Also, investigate the effects associated with dose tapering of TNF-α inhibitors.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
